data.name: PFLASTERS
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- Made of Elastic, PE, PU and Spunlace fabric
- Adhesive: Solvent, Acrylic and Hotmelt

## STERILIZATION
- Non-Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- Various Patterns and Colors
- Various Shapes and Finishes
- With and without Haemostatic Island
- Packagings: Hospital and Phamacy

## PERFORMANCE
- Skin friendly
- Aseptic, non-sterile
- Hypoallergenic
- Strong hold without skin irritation (Latex-free)
